### 1. Login ca ADMIN
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

> {% client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.token); %}


### 2. Login ca USER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "user"
}

> {% client.global.set("user_token", response.body.token); %}


### 3. Adăugare produs (ADMIN only)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "price": 1500.0
}


### 4. Lista produse (ADMIN allowed)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 5. Detalii produs (ADMIN allowed)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 6. Modificare preț produs (ADMIN only)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/products/1/price
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "price": 1200.0
}


### 7. Ștergere produs (ADMIN only)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 8. Lista produse (USER allowed)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}


### 9. Detalii produs (USER allowed)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}


